<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0218a" xml:id="I01.0081.0218a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0218a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 81</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0218a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>雷暉嫗造釋迦像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0219a" xml:id="I01.0081.0219a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0219a00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0219a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0219a0101">大周保定五年歲次乙酉五月
<lb ed="I" n="0219a02"/>壬午朔五日丙戌。
<lb ed="I" n="0219a03"/>雷暉嫗者。三門護軍王□之孫。
<lb ed="I" n="0219a04"/>功曹張郎之女也。父祖相承。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0219001" n="0219001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0219001" n="0219001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0219001" n="0219001"/>關<anchor xml:id="end0219001"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0219a05"/>中豪族。歷代酋<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0219002" n="0219002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0219002" n="0219002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0219002" n="0219002"/>望<anchor xml:id="end0219002"/>。軀雖受女身。
<lb ed="I" n="0219a06"/>志性真明。殊懷丈夫之<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0219003" n="0219003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0219003" n="0219003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0219003" n="0219003"/>操<anchor xml:id="end0219003"/>。五德
<lb ed="I" n="0219a07"/>六藏。體會而能標女儀婦道。動成
<lb ed="I" n="0219a08"/>於物軌。年在初笄。從禮而□□
<lb ed="I" n="0219a09"/>門□字□□。本是□州河東郡
<lb ed="I" n="0219a10"/>蒲坂縣人也。忩朗令哲。譏會無
<lb ed="I" n="0219a11"/>方。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">覽</unclear>練<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">眾</unclear>經。內<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">外</unclear>斯朗。於神龜
<lb ed="I" n="0219a12"/>年中。跨滻河□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">觀</unclear>矚<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">跛</unclear>□
<lb ed="I" n="0219a13"/><anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>關<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>隴優遊西□□氏慕德因□
<lb ed="I" n="0219a14"/>為親繾綣。一生事同魚□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0219a15"/>永熙之季。海內□遶魏□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0219a16"/>英豪岳□□□□方欲<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0219004" n="0219004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0219004" n="0219004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0219004" n="0219004"/>掃<anchor xml:id="end0219004"/>定<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">宇</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0219a17"/>宙。廣募賢良猛<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">騎</unclear>。時忠勇奮發。□
<lb ed="I" n="0219a18"/>□□應命。即除龍驤將軍。□□</p></cb:div></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0219b" xml:id="I01.0081.0219b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0219b00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　碑側</cb:mulu><head>之二　碑側</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0219b01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0219b0101">□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□有壹子。字令業。長成□□□有<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0219005" n="0219005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0219005" n="0219005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0219005" n="0219005"/>父<anchor xml:id="end0219005"/>風。文經武略。庶
<lb ed="I" n="0219b02"/>□□□□□□□□□□年中。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0219006" n="0219006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0219006" n="0219006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0219006" n="0219006"/>寢<anchor xml:id="end0219006"/>疾而終。凡在親知。愛其父子仁義□□。莫不留戀。嫗<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0219007" n="0219007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0219007" n="0219007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0219007" n="0219007"/>愍<anchor xml:id="end0219007"/>之□息
<lb ed="I" n="0219b03"/>□□□□□□□塗三塬。三塬者。天地初開。伏羲之<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0219008" n="0219008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0219008" n="0219008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0219008" n="0219008"/>舊<anchor xml:id="end0219008"/>名。往古來今。聖賢之所都邑。皆無凶咎。遂
<lb ed="I" n="0219b04"/>□□父子同<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">埒</unclear>。精靈莫二。其墳上高十尺。下至黃泉。棺槨相重。儭幣自周。蒔柏卅餘□。并諸□□
<lb ed="I" n="0219b05"/>有□春<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">冬</unclear>□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">變</unclear>。又仰憑　三寶。有濟度之能。敬造釋加石像前後兩堪。并諸聖之像。□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0219b06"/>□。等同斯福。法界含生。□登正道。物之堅固者。莫過金石。署碑於墓。永存．．．</p></cb:div></cb:div>
</body>
